    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An unstandardized name referring to slightly greenish yellow pigments including but not confined to barium chromate, strontium chromate, zinc chromate, chrome yellow, and zinc yellow, or several organic yellow colorants.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
